BAPS Shri Swaminarayan Temple Nagpur is a famous Temple and one of the most remarkable buildings in Nagpur.
BAPS Shri Swaminarayan Mandir Nagpur is situated at Swaminarayan marg middle ring road Wathoda Nagpur. The entry tickets to BAPS Swaminarayan Temple nagpur is free. BAPS
Swaminarayan Temple Nagpur is visited daily by thousands of devotees for Murti darshan and to view the design & architecture of this famous temple. ……………………Must Visit Place in Nagpur.  Swaminarayan marg middle ring road Wathoda
